    "Moreover, one could imagine that given the appropriate resourses (funding and time), the treshhold could be decreased from the currently 80.1% to render still more useful mixtures.",
    "In addition, it is worth mentioning that the formation and physicochemical properties of the NADES formed depend not only on the chemical nature of its components but also on the strength of the intermolecular interactions formed at specific molar ratios.",
